      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、いる？\n入ってもいいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ are you there?\nCan I come in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5900,
          "startTime": 8.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6100,
          "startTime": 8.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 4.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 4.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "神崎さん？　どうぞ\nみんなの様子はどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that you‚ Rio-san? Go ahead.\nHow is everyone doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "最初は落ち込んだりもしてたけど、大丈夫よ\n気を持ち直して、レッスンしているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They were depressed at first‚ but they’re okay now.\nThey’ve picked themselves up and are taking lessons right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 17.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、貴方の方が重症のようね\nしっかりしなさいよ、星見プロの現代表でしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything‚ it looks like you suffered more damage.\nPull yourself together. Aren’t you the president of Hoshimi Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 24.666666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "代理ですけどね……\nすいません、情けないところを見せてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Acting president…\nSorry. I didn’t want you to see me in this state.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "何もかもが後手に回ってしまった\nそのせいでトリエルを苦しめたことが、悔しくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just seem to be one step behind in everything.\nI feel so guilty about letting TRINITYAiLE suffer as a result.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 38.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、落ち込む気持ちは分かるけどね\n私も、貴方の立場だったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I can understand why you feel down.\nIf I were in your position‚ I would.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、だからこそシャキッとしなさい\n代表が暗いと、みんなも暗くなるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s why you need to pull yourself together.\nIf the leader is depressed‚ everyone will be depressed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 52.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、三枝さんに笑われるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ Saegusa-san will be disappointed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 56.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……ありがとうございます。もう大丈夫です\n神崎さんは俺を励ましに来てくれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. Thank you. I’m okay now.\nDid you come here to cheer me up‚ Kanzaki-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "それだけじゃないわ\n単刀直入に、結論から言うわね。私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just that.\nI’ll be direct and get straight to the point.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 72.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "正式に、星見プロへ移籍するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to officially transfer to Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 75.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　いや、でも\nすでに契約は交わしているから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But‚ uh‚\nwe’ve already signed the contract…Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hope-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 80.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 80.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、書面上はね\nでも違うの。これは気持ちの問題",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ on paper.\nBut that’s not it. This is a matter of the heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 87.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "これまでは、自分の活動の場さえ得られるなら\n所属先は正直どこでもいいと思ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Up until now‚ I figured as long as they’d give me stages to perform in‚\nthat it didn’t matter which agency I was signed under.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "けど姫野さんのやり方を見て、ハッキリ分かったわ\nあの人の下じゃ、正々堂々トップを目指せない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now that I’ve seen how Himeno-san does things‚ it’s become clear.\nIf I work for her‚ I will never be able to aim for the top‚ fair and square.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 104.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "正々堂々、トップを目指す。それが\n神崎さんにとって、とても大切なことなんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aim for the top‚ fair and square…\nThat’s very important to you‚ isn’t it‚ Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 112.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。頂点に立って、ファンに、仲間に……\nそして母に胸を張れるアイドルになりたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. When I stand at the top before my fans‚ my fellow idols…\nand my mother‚ I want to be able to take pride in the idol I am.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 122.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんは、確かに優秀だったかもしれない\nけど、やり方にはいつも違和感を覚えていたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Himeno-san probably was the superior choice.\nBut something about the way she did business never sat right with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの実力とは違うところで勝負を仕掛け\n勝ちを得ようとする考え方に、私は馴染めなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’d try to score victories by means other than an idol’s talent.\nThat way of thinking just didn’t mesh with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 138.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、神崎さんの思う正々堂々なやり方じゃない\nそれでも表面上はうまく回っていた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that’s not the “fair and square” method you like.\nBut on the surface‚ it looked like everything was going well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "これまでは朝倉さんが、裏で筋を通していたんだろう\nけど彼がいなくなって、姫野さんは暴走している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess‚ up until now‚ Asakura-san stuck to his principles behind the scenes.\nBut now that he’s gone‚ Himeno-san is running wild.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 155.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_07_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "いずれにせよ、私はもうバンプロには戻らないわ\n正々堂々とトップを目指せる最高の環境は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In any case‚ I won’t be returning to Van Productions.\nI believe the best place for me to aim for the top‚ fair and square…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 163.43333333333334
